data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Fountain, Colorado! This stunning tri-level residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and modern amenities. With 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a range of recent upgrades, this home is ready to welcome you with open arms.  Step inside and be greeted by the beautifully updated kitchen, featuring new stainless steel appliances that will delight any culinary enthusiast. The under cabinet lighting adds a touch of elegance and creates an inviting atmosphere. The adjacent dining area is perfect for enjoying meals with family and friends.  Feel the plush new carpet beneath your feet as you explore the spacious living areas. The open layout provides seamless flow and abundant natural light, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Cozy up on chilly evenings by the fireplace, creating memorable moments with loved ones.  The master bedroom is a true retreat, boasting dual master closets for ample storage space and organization. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide flexibility for guests, a home office, or a growing family.  The charm continues outdoors with a back patio, perfect for outdoor entertaining or enjoying a peaceful morning coffee. The patio also features a gazebo, providing shade and an inviting space for relaxation.  A highlight of this home is the walkout unfinished basement, offering endless possibilities for customization and expansion. Whether you envision a home gym, a recreation room, or extra storage, this blank canvas awaits your creative touch.  Rest easy knowing that this home has a new roof, ensuring durability and peace of mind. Additionally, the attention to detail and modern upgrades throughout make this property truly move-in ready.  Conveniently located in Fountain, Colorado, you'll enjoy easy access to local amenities, parks, schools, and more. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours!    Welcome home!
